{"tid":857123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本東京新宿特輯狂放送范冰冰  中國人驚呆了","createTime":"2018-10-11T02:34:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T05:53:40.000Z","uid":184679,"like":197,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"5aa00a024de2d8b9ad78ef200758245f78d81162","tid":857123,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T02:34:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2018/10/11/phpfbEGxJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2018%2F10%2F11%2FphpfbEGxJ.png&h=61d4436a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本東京新宿街頭近日不斷放送范冰冰逃稅事件新聞。（星島日報）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n37歲中國女星范冰冰捲入「陰陽合同」逃稅案震驚全球，因她曾接拍好萊塢電影名氣響亮，連歐美國家的媒體也有報導。多次為主演電影到日本宣傳的范冰冰，在當地曾被封為「美艷女神」，有日媒昨驚曝她可能在12月復出。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，近來日媒高度關注范冰冰受追查神隱一事，曾以長達2分鐘特輯剖析范冰冰逃稅案，報導此案牽連不少藝人，重創中國娛樂事業。誇張的是，日本有關范冰冰特輯報導，連日來被安排在東京新宿街頭巨型電視螢幕播放。由於新宿是中國遊客的旅遊熱點，不少中國人都有看到，看完不禁搖著憤怒離去。<br />\n<br />\n值得關注的是，這幾天被指密謀復出的范冰冰，近期不時在微博現身，還在線上跟粉絲聊天，昨有日媒驚爆，范冰冰將於12月正式復出，顯見日本媒體高度關注她的動向。<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2577184[/url\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2577184%5B%2Furl&d=axA5DrRCs4Vnxv9RK5h5QaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=4d291cf0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2577184%5B%2Furl&h=28b70932\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2577184[/url</a>"},{"pid":"c8e08624e4ca649a176e082bd75f0ec01ba277de","tid":857123,"uid":45518,"like":429,"dislike":2,"score":427,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T02:37:11.000Z","msg":"不少中國人都有看到，看完不禁搖著憤怒離去<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"286e258c8a6778a7f8fdc5dace7c68c244a9f814","tid":857123,"uid":184679,"like":416,"dislike":2,"score":414,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T02:37:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">日網民：見到佢個名即刻硬哂</span><br />\n<br />\n范冰冰喺國內外知名度都好高，所以唔止歐美傳媒有報道此事，就連日本方面亦非常關注事件。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/NjTbpyR5aQZywz07jkgKVw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/orientalsundayent.com/21a0b383c528d15d38f75e080095f257\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FNjTbpyR5aQZywz07jkgKVw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Forientalsundayent.com%2F21a0b383c528d15d38f75e080095f257&h=8c46e166&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過一聽到范冰冰呢個名，班日本網民諗到嘅就同大家關注嘅嘢好唔同啦！因為冰冰嘅日文譯音（ビンビン），讀出嚟係binbin，亦即係「勃起」咁解。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AC%A1%E6%80%A7%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93-%E8%8C%83%E5%86%B0%E5%86%B0%E6%97%A5%E6%96%87%E8%AD%AF%E9%9F%B3%E7%AB%9F%E6%9C%89%E6%80%A7%E6%9A%97%E7%A4%BA-%E6%97%A5%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-%E8%A6%8B%E5%88%B0%E4%BD%A2%E5%80%8B%E5%90%8D%E5%8D%B3%E5%88%BB%E7%A1%AC%E5%93%82-100927803.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E6%2580%25A7%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%2598%2593-%25E8%258C%2583%25E5%2586%25B0%25E5%2586%25B0%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%2596%2587%25E8%25AD%25AF%25E9%259F%25B3%25E7%25AB%259F%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2580%25A7%25E6%259A%2597%25E7%25A4%25BA-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591-%25E8%25A6%258B%25E5%2588%25B0%25E4%25BD%25A2%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%258D%25B3%25E5%2588%25BB%25E7%25A1%25AC%25E5%2593%2582-100927803.html&d=axA5DrRCs4Vnxv9RK5h5QaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=5fa77011\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AC%A1%E6%80%A7%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93-%E8%8C%83%E5%86%B0%E5%86%B0%E6%97%A5%E6%96%87%E8%AD%AF%E9%9F%B3%E7%AB%9F%E6%9C%89%E6%80%A7%E6%9A%97%E7%A4%BA-%E6%97%A5%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-%E8%A6%8B%E5%88%B0%E4%BD%A2%E5%80%8B%E5%90%8D%E5